					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Speech synthesizer SAM ran in real time on the 1 MHz 6502 in Apple II and C64. The SPC700 is a 1 MHz 65C02 with a reshuffled instruction encoding and a minor difference in the PLA instruction.</div>

